text: Miss Earth 2018 is the 18th edition of the Miss Earth pageant. Karen Ibasco of the Philippines crowned Nguyễn Phương Khánh of Vietnam on November 3, 2018. == Results == Result Contestant Represented Miss Earth 2018 Nguyễn Phương Khánh Miss Earth – Air 2018
